  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cut the Fluffy sheets into 2-inch squares.",
    "In a bowl, mix together Greek Cheese, Tiropita, Feta Cheese, Egg, Salt, and Black Pepper.",
    "Place a spoonful of the cheese mixture onto the center of each Fluffy square.",
    "Brush the edges with milk and fold the Fluffy squares to form triangles.",
    "Place the triangles on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake for 15-20 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
